to see clear distinctions

00:13:47.440 --> 00:13:52.580 align:middle line:84%
between similar things, even
down to their micro differences.

00:13:52.580 --> 00:13:56.920 align:middle line:84%
So this capacity is a
spiritual nuance in perception

00:13:56.920 --> 00:14:00.710 align:middle line:84%
that gives us command
over our perception,

00:14:00.710 --> 00:14:03.370 align:middle line:84%
and that is the dominant
function of the third eye

00:14:03.370 --> 00:14:04.340 align:middle line:90%
chakra.

00:14:04.340 --> 00:14:07.180 align:middle line:84%
It is our spiritual
sight beyond the vision

00:14:07.180 --> 00:14:09.380 align:middle line:90%
of our two physical eyes.

00:14:09.380 --> 00:14:12.880 align:middle line:84%
This chakra pierces
through all illusions

00:14:12.880 --> 00:14:16.390 align:middle line:84%
in order to perceive
what is real and true.

00:14:16.390 --> 00:14:20.410 align:middle line:10%
So the third eye either
sees or senses a phenomenon

00:14:20.410 --> 00:14:22.510 align:middle line:10%
