00:15:57.900 --> 00:16:01.530 align:middle line:84%
That is what this energy
center represents.

00:16:01.530 --> 00:16:04.640 align:middle line:84%
It is the omnipresent
invisible knowing

00:16:04.640 --> 00:16:07.700 align:middle line:84%
from being directly connected
with our higher self

00:16:07.700 --> 00:16:09.920 align:middle line:90%
