We usually have some
ambient energies

00:16:22.370 --> 00:16:25.200 align:middle line:84%
that we sense around
the crown center.

00:16:25.200 --> 00:16:29.000 align:middle line:84%
So this energy center
is the one that we

00:16:29.000 --> 00:16:32.610 align:middle line:84%
could look at as being
source consciousness,

00:16:32.610 --> 00:16:36.830 align:middle line:90%
but through the physical senses.

00:16:36.830 --> 00:16:40.850 align:middle line:84%
This is where we experience
our true divine nature

00:16:40.850 --> 00:16:44.280 align:middle line:84%
and our true
identity as divinity,

00:16:44.280 --> 00:16:47.540 align:middle line:84%
and how we receive information
through this center

00:16:47.540 --> 00:16:51.290 align:middle line:90%
