00:16:51.290 --> 00:16:55.520 align:middle line:84%
So many times we
equate crown chakra

00:16:55.520 --> 00:16:59.060 align:middle line:84%
activations or even
claircognizance

00:16:59.060 --> 00:17:04.099 align:middle line:84%
as an all-knowing ability,
when in reality, it's

00:17:04.099 --> 00:17:10.349 align:middle line:84%
an ability that gives us more
knowing when we're in motion,

00:17:10.349 --> 00:17:15.180 align:middle line:84%
when we need it, when we are
at that part of our own journey

00:17:15.180 --> 00:17:17.359 align:middle line:90%
when we're ready to receive it.

00:17:17.359 --> 00:17:19.880 align:middle line:84%
And that's what's so
important to understand

00:17:19.880 --> 00:17:21.660 align:middle line:90%
about claircognizance.

00:17:21.660 --> 00:17:24.660 align:middle line:84%
It's that instead of it
being an all-knowing,

00:17:24.660 --> 00:17:26.830 align:middle line:84%
it's more of when
we need to know.

