So all of the chakras
have a distinct identity

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:38.600 align:middle line:84%
and a distinct truth
that even represents

00:17:38.600 --> 00:17:41.840 align:middle line:84%
all of the dimensions
of our energy field

00:17:41.840 --> 00:17:45.500 align:middle line:84%
and all of the different
truths that our energy field

00:17:45.500 --> 00:17:50.210 align:middle line:84%
holds to make up
our ability to be

00:17:50.210 --> 00:17:54.350 align:middle line:84%
a physical and
spiritual identity here

00:17:54.350 --> 00:17:57.200 align:middle line:90%
in the physical realm.

00:17:57.200 --> 00:18:01.160 align:middle line:10%
How we can nurture the
development of these chakras

