to their highest capacity.

00:20:18.526 --> 00:20:21.860 align:middle line:90%


00:20:21.860 --> 00:20:25.890 align:middle line:84%
Chakras function together
as an entire network.

00:20:25.890 --> 00:20:29.900 align:middle line:84%
They are our energy fields
holistic distributors of life

00:20:29.900 --> 00:20:31.520 align:middle line:90%
force and prana.

00:20:31.520 --> 00:20:34.680 align:middle line:84%
What this means is that they
are not isolated channels

00:20:34.680 --> 00:20:35.830 align:middle line:90%
of life force.

00:20:35.830 --> 00:20:38.920 align:middle line:84%
They respond and
react to one another.

00:20:38.920 --> 00:20:42.610 align:middle line:10%
If one chakra is experiencing
a certain impairment,

00:20:42.610 --> 00:20:45.780 align:middle line:10%
another chakra will start
to move out of balance

00:20:45.780 --> 00:20:47.530 align:middle line:10%
to lend its resources.

00:20:47.530 --> 00:20:49.950 align:middle line:10%
This creates a
domino effect, where

00:20:49.950 --> 00:20:54.240 align:middle line:10%
each chakra becomes directly
impacted by the other's blocks

00:20:54.240 --> 00:20:57.240 align:middle line:10%
and has to overcompensate
in some way.

00:20:57.240 --> 00:21:00.870 align:middle line:10%
How the chakras become
imbalanced by overcompensating

00:21:00.870 --> 00:21:04.920 align:middle line:10%
for one another will be
personal to each of us.

00:21:04.920 --> 00:21:07.890 align:middle line:84%
We can harmonize the
entire chakra network

00:21:07.890 --> 00:21:10.710 align:middle line:84%
through a powerful
mantra that brings them

00:21:10.710 --> 00:21:14.800 align:middle line:84%
all into alignment and with
resonance with each other,

00:21:14.800 --> 00:21:18.330 align:middle line:84%
just like a tuning fork
produces a fixed tone.

00:21:18.330 --> 00:21:36.120 align:middle line:84%
