RAM, YAM HAM, AUM, OM.

00:21:36.120 --> 00:21:37.980 align:middle line:84%
When we say that
all together, it

00:21:37.980 --> 00:21:49.800 align:middle line:84%
goes LAM, VAM, RAM,
YAM, HAM, AUM, OM.

00:21:49.800 --> 00:21:52.350 align:middle line:84%
This mantra is a
very powerful tool

00:21:52.350 --> 00:21:56.490 align:middle line:84%
to align the entire
chakra network.

